      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm a consultant working with some C-suite execs who are pretty skeptical about the new DEI initiatives being pushed. They want to be prepared for the upcoming board meeting. Can you help me outline the strongest arguments against affirmative action? They're mostly looking for the case for a pure \"race-blind meritocracy\" and why they think current diversity programs might actually be unfair to certain groups.",
